    {
      "_id": "DLvBHgdOJzRqlLhd",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "<strong>Falling block.</strong> A stone block drops in the doorway as it opens — save vs. paralysis (or Dexterity) or take 2d6 damage. <em>Circumvent:</em> Search to spot the seam; brace/wedge the block; trigger it from the side with a pole.",
      "img": "icons/svg/trap.svg",
