      "type": "text",
      "text": "<strong>Alarm (gong or bell).</strong> Opening rings a hidden bell or gong — make a wandering-monster check, and anything nearby is alerted. <em>Circumvent:</em> Spot and muffle the wire/clapper; oil the hinges; pick the lock quietly and ease the door.",
