      "type": "text",
      "text": "<strong>Pit beneath the threshold.</strong> The floor in the doorway drops as the door swings — fall 10 ft (1d6) or more. <em>Circumvent:</em> Tap the floor ahead with a pole; open the door and step back; lay a plank across.",
