      "text": "<strong>Gas jet (sleep or poison).</strong> A jet of gas vents from the frame — save vs. poison or fall asleep / be sickened. <em>Circumvent:</em> Hold your breath and back away; detect and plug the nozzle; pull the door open from a distance with a rope.",
